verbose_text: Injection of let-7d agomir significantly elevated the levels of p62 and reduced the ratio of LC3-II to LC3-I compared with injection of agomir NC (P < 0.05), while injection of the let-7d antagomir significantly decreased the levels of p62 and increased the ratio of LC3-II to LC3-I (P < 0.05) compared with injection of the antagomir NC (XREF_FIG).
